24:37.543 --> 24:39.243
Oh, honey, he told me to.

24:39.245 --> 24:41.145
You know,
you're all he talks about.

24:41.147 --> 24:43.481
I think he thought
maybe it might be better

24:43.483 --> 24:46.750
if it came from some kind
of a neutral party, you know?

24:46.752 --> 24:48.252
See this?

24:48.254 --> 24:50.855
He built that for me.

24:50.857 --> 24:53.824
I met him under this bridge.

24:55.261 --> 24:57.595
He should have
sent it himself.

24:57.597 --> 24:59.763
Oh, honey, he's sick.

24:59.765 --> 25:02.533
He's always been sick.

25:02.535 --> 25:05.069
You see that behind you there?

25:05.071 --> 25:08.772
Now, he said
he carved that for me.

25:08.774 --> 25:11.175
But that's not my face, right?

25:11.177 --> 25:14.979
That's your face.
That's not me.

25:14.981 --> 25:18.516
He always used to carve
things like this.

25:18.518 --> 25:21.852
He's got cancer, Fern.

25:21.854 --> 25:23.721
What?

25:23.723 --> 25:25.990
Doesn't wanna go
to a hospital.

25:25.992 --> 25:28.192
He's gonna let it
finish him.

25:28.194 --> 25:30.194
That's why I wrote you
the note.

25:40.806 --> 25:43.807
When was the last time
you saw him?

25:43.809 --> 25:47.278
About two weeks ago,
I guess.

25:47.280 --> 25:49.280
There's a place called
Murphy's Ranch.

25:49.282 --> 25:51.315
It's one of his favorite spots.
It's up in Topanga.

25:51.317 --> 25:55.719
Were you two at all...

25:55.721 --> 25:58.656
Yes, we were.

25:58.658 --> 26:02.927
He's a hard man
to hang onto.

26:02.929 --> 26:05.930
Maybe I was better off
without him.

26:05.932 --> 26:07.932
Now, if you believe that,

26:07.934 --> 26:09.700
you wouldn't have
gotten in your car,

26:09.702 --> 26:11.802
come all the way down here,
now, would you, huh?

26:16.809 --> 26:19.944
You have to see your father.
He should see you again.

26:19.946 --> 26:22.947
He should see what a lovely
young lady you've become.

26:26.786 --> 26:28.185
It was nice meeting you,
Dr. Green.

26:28.187 --> 26:30.988
No, you don't have to go yet.

26:30.990 --> 26:33.090
We can't waste any more time.

26:33.092 --> 26:36.860
Well, listen, kids,
if you need anything,

26:36.862 --> 26:39.229
you need anything at all...

26:40.900 --> 26:42.933
Oh, I can't believe
you're here.

26:42.935 --> 26:45.202
I just can't believe it.

26:45.204 --> 26:46.971
If you need anything,
you call me.

26:46.973 --> 26:49.139
You come right here.
You come right here.

26:49.141 --> 26:50.774
- Thanks.
- You have any questions--

26:50.776 --> 26:52.209
We will. Thanks.

26:52.211 --> 26:54.712
- You know where to find me.
- Okay.

26:58.150 --> 26:59.183
WYATT: Hey.

27:00.286 --> 27:02.786
Do you really have a PhD?

27:02.788 --> 27:06.757
Berkeley '71,
Philosophy.

27:06.759 --> 27:09.927
You be careful of her.
She's like her papa.

27:43.796 --> 27:47.698
