Maybe he's here.

30:56.422 --> 30:58.188
Goddamn it!

31:16.008 --> 31:18.175
I just want him to be real.

31:18.177 --> 31:20.444
I promise he's real.

31:35.427 --> 31:38.495
What just happened?
Is this a joke?

31:38.497 --> 31:41.565
Wyatt, Wyatt.

31:41.567 --> 31:43.367
Are you okay? Wyatt!

31:43.369 --> 31:46.270
- [snoring]
- Huh?

31:53.279 --> 31:55.145
This is embarrassing.

32:00.252 --> 32:02.519
What the fuck was that?

32:03.923 --> 32:05.322
I fell asleep.

32:06.458 --> 32:08.091
Wow.

32:08.093 --> 32:09.459
That boring, huh?

32:09.461 --> 32:11.061
Narcolepsy.

32:11.063 --> 32:13.563
Seriously?
Why didn't you tell me?

32:13.565 --> 32:15.098
You just scared the crap
out of me.

32:15.100 --> 32:16.700
I thought I had a handle on it.

32:16.702 --> 32:18.368
Jesus.

32:18.370 --> 32:21.438
It only happens when I get
emotionally triggered.

32:21.440 --> 32:23.707
How do you drive?

32:23.709 --> 32:25.976
I don't know.
I try to stay calm,

32:25.978 --> 32:28.946
listen to smooth jazz,

32:28.948 --> 32:30.714
avoid road rage.

32:32.518 --> 32:35.485
You know, when I was a kid
in like school,

32:35.487 --> 32:38.422
all the students would just try
to get me so riled up and angry

32:38.424 --> 32:41.258
so I'd pass out and wake up

32:41.260 --> 32:45.162
with a bunch of
marker drawings on my face.

32:45.164 --> 32:48.732
- Aw, that's so terrible.
- I know.

32:48.734 --> 32:52.035
Wait, does this mean
that you're gonna fall asleep

32:52.037 --> 32:54.004
every time we kiss?

32:54.006 --> 32:56.206
I guess we'll just
have to find out.

33:01.547 --> 33:03.747
- You look alert.
- Yeah?

33:03.749 --> 33:05.449
[shouting]

33:05.451 --> 33:06.984
Jesus!

33:10.556 --> 33:12.522
Sorry. I thought
you were park rangers.

33:12.524 --> 33:14.157
We didn't see anything.
We're not gonna tell anybody.

33:14.159 --> 33:15.525
What do you think I'm doing?

33:15.527 --> 33:18.161
Do you think
I'm making meth in there?

33:18.163 --> 33:21.765
Goddamn it! I'm tired of
people thinking that

33:21.767 --> 33:23.533
just 'cause of the way I look!

33:23.535 --> 33:27.471
What about me says
I'm making meth?

33:29.508 --> 33:31.208
It's not what I'm making!

33:31.210 --> 33:33.477
What are you making then?

33:33.479 --> 33:36.613
Making angel dust, PCP.
It's not meth.

33:36.615 --> 33:39.149
That's gross, you know?

33:39.151 --> 33:42.019
It's not a big deal.
Gotta make something.

33:42.021 --> 33:44.321
It's hard to get a job
out there for a felon.

33:44.323 --> 33:45.722
We understand.

33:45.724 --> 33:47.324
Yeah, no, we're not
judging you at all.

33:48.627 --> 33:51.361
Thank you.
Actually, that...

33:51.363 --> 33:53.497
You actually don't even know
how much that means.

33:53.499 --> 33:55.098
I need to hear that sometimes.

33:55.100 --> 33:56.199
WYATT: You're welcome.

33:56.201 --> 33:59.136
Do you wanna buy some?

33:59.138 --> 34:02.072
Do you know a guy named Simon
who lives out here sometimes?

34:02.074 --> 34:03.540
Yeah, I know him.

34:03.542 --> 34:05.242
Haven't seen him
in a few weeks though.

34:05.244 --> 34:07.744
If you see him,
that bastard owes me money.

34:07.746 --> 34:09.546
This homeless powder
isn't free.

34:09.548 --> 34:11.314
He does PCP?

34:11.316 --> 34:12.349
[chuckles]

34:12.351 --> 34:14.718
He dabbles.

34:14.720 --> 34:16.753
You should try
the Star Hotel downtown.

34:16.755 --> 34:18.655
