with the other degenerates.

34:18.657 --> 34:19.823
Thanks.

34:19.825 --> 34:22.659
Hey...

34:22.661 --> 34:25.095
you're not gonna tell anyone
about me, are you?

34:25.097 --> 34:28.598
We have no idea where we are,
so that would be impossible.

34:28.600 --> 34:32.135
I trust you guys to keep my
clandestine drug lab a secret.

34:32.137 --> 34:33.303
Really?

34:33.305 --> 34:34.571
